    dc:description "Figure 7. Characters of the Crematogaster inflata-group. A, mesosoma in profile view (C. difformis). B, mesosoma in profile view (C. mucronata). C, mesosoma in profile view (C. Ʋacca). D, arrow indicates comma-shaped metapleural gland opening in dorsolateral view (C. subcircularis)." ;
